user.biography: We’re your Ultimate Sports Lodge. It’s where you come to watch every game in HD, the beer is an icy 29° and the food leaves you coming back for more.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Twin Peaks Restaurant on August 13, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and standing.

node.text: Premier League soccer is back! Come kick it with us for the game and catch Brentford take on Arsenal at 2pm CST, followed by a weekend jam packed with matches. #PremierLeague #Soccer #TwinPeaks #ComeKickIt

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Twin Peaks Restaurant on August 11, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing, drink and indoor.

node.text: Happy Wednesday🍻 We hope to see you today for $3.75 Signature Beers on special ALL DAY! #TwinPeaks #TwinPeaksRestaurants

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Twin Peaks Restaurant on August 09, 2021. May be an image of food and text.

node.text: Have you heard we added a new wing sauce to our lineup? Try out the Bourbon Teriyaki, featuring Sweet Garlic Teriyaki and Wild Turkey 101 Bourbon. #TwinPeaks #TwinPeaksRestaurant #BourbonTeriyaki #WildTurkey #Wings

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Twin Peaks Restaurant on August 09, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text: At Twin Peaks, we're proud to partner with Pets for Patriots. Pets for Patriots is dedicated to helping veterans adopt pets and shelter animals find loving homes. So how can you help? Enjoy a glass of wine with us! Every single wine purchase you make with us funnels into a contribution on our behalf. We'll drink to that. #Cheers #Wine #PetsforPatriots

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Twin Peaks Restaurant on August 08, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and text.

node.text:
FIND YOUR PEAKS!
TEXT WORK4TP TO 85000!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Twin Peaks Restaurant on August 08, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and drink.

node.text: It’s your last chance to watch the Olympics at the lodge, so come in and watch our greatest athletes on the big screen. #TwinPeaks #TwinPeaksRestaurant #Olympics #USA #TokyoOlympics

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Twin Peaks Restaurant on August 07, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, indoor and text that says 'UFC 265 LEWIS INTERIM HEAVYWEIGHT CHAMPIONSHIP GANE AUG 7 SAT TOYOTA CENTER'.

node.text: Tonight: UFC 265 is going down! The man with 20 knockouts, Derrick Lewis, takes on undefeated Ciryl Gane in the Heavyweight Interim Title Bout. Get here for every second of knockout action! Contact your favorite location for availability and cover info. #TwinPeaks #TwinPeaksRestaurant #UFC265 #UFC

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Twin Peaks Restaurant on August 07, 2021. May be an image of 3 people, drink, indoor and text that says 'm BUT IGH GHT Modelo BUD LIGHT'.

node.text: Get to Twin Peaks every Saturday and Sunday for our buckets of beer on special $13 for domestics $16 for imports!

node.text: What better way to celebrate International Beer Day than with the coldest draft in town? Come get your 29° beer today. #TwinPeaks #TwinPeaksRestaurant #InternationalBeerDay #29DegreeBeer

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Twin Peaks Restaurant on August 05, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing, drink and indoor.

node.text: It’s National IPA Day and our signature IPA, the Drop Dead Redhead, has the flavorful hops you’re searching for. #TwinPeaks #TwinPeaksRestaurant #NationalIPADay #Beer

node.text: Are you ready for some football? Finally – the NFL is back! Come catch the Cowboys and Steelers kick off the official NFL Preseason with this year’s Hall of Fame Game at 8:00pm EST. Let’s go! #TwinPeaks #TwinPeaksRestaurant #Cowboys #Buccaneers #NFL #Football
